Invocation Name: a. i. facts
des:
Ask for AI Facts, and learn about what buzz words like "Neural Networks" mean.

AI Facts provides information on AI that will alow you to understand what any buzzwords mean.

To start, just say "Alexa, launch AI Facts" or "Alexa, open AI Facts" to get a fact".

At anytime, you can stop by saying "Alexa, stop"
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
